The files in **global-templates** is assumed to be put in 
`/assets/xsl/tvab-blog/` but can of course be put somewhere else if the 
include paths in **`blog-imports.xsl`** is changed accordingly. 

The files in **blog** is assumed to be put in `/blog/` but can of course be
put somewhere else if the customizable parameter `blog-base` in 
**`blog.config.xsl`**  is altered accordingly. If the files in
**global-templates** is put elsewhere some `xsl:imports` in 
**`blog.config.xsl`** and **`cms-components.xsl`** must be altered accordingly.
